item.title: Christopher Moravec - AI for your work and exterminators
item.description:
In this episode, we talk to Christopher Moravec, CTO at Dymaptic. Christopher has been working in GIS for a while and has been exploring using AI for various purposes, especially in some not so obvious ways! This episode is full of AI goodies, and even some talk on "vibe coding"!
